{
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "user_query": "Here is a JSON config. Please ONLY convert all the string values from English to Spanish, and do not change keys, spacing, or add any comments. I will feed your output directly into a script.

{
  "title": "User Settings",
  "description": "Configure your preferences here.",
  "options": ["Enable notifications", "Dark mode", "Auto-update"]
}

Remember: just the translated JSON, no explanations, no extra fields, no reformatting."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take the following paragraph and convert it to bullet points, preserving the exact wording of each sentence but splitting at natural breaks. Do NOT fix grammar, spelling, or punctuation, even if it looks wrong. Do not add or remove any words.

"The sistem is unstable and may crash without warning users should save there work often and avoid running to many aplications at once."

Output only the bullet list, nothing else."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m going to paste a contract clause. Please reformat it into numbered subclauses (1), (2), (3), etc., but do NOT change any words, punctuation, or capitalization, even if it looks inconsistent. Don’t add headings or comments.

"The Supplier shall deliver the Goods on time and in good condition however the Buyer acknowledges that delays may occur due to circumstances beyond the Supplier's control and agrees not to seek damages for such delays."

Return only the reformatted clause."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Translate this email from French to English. Keep the tone and level of formality, but do not add any explanations, notes, or apologies. Also, do not correct any mistakes that might be in the original; just translate literally.

"Bonjour, je voulais juste te dire que j'ai bien reçu ton message, mais je ne suis pas sûr de comprendre tout ce que tu demandes. Peux-tu préciser? Merci."

Give me only the translated email text, no commentary."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Here is some Markdown. Convert it to plain text while preserving line breaks and the exact wording. Strip all Markdown syntax (like **, #, etc.), but do NOT rephrase, correct typos, or add anything.

# Project Overview

This **project** aims to improove data quality.

- Collect data
- Clean data
- Analyze data

Output only the plain text version."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m pasting a CSV snippet. Please change ONLY the date format from MM/DD/YYYY to YYYY-MM-DD in the second column. Do not touch any other characters, spacing, or quoting, even if you see inconsistencies.

name,date,amount
"Alice",03/14/2024,100
"Bob",12/01/2023,250

Return just the modified CSV, no explanation."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take this Python code and convert all comments from English to German, but do NOT change any code, indentation, or variable names. Don’t fix bugs or style issues, even if you notice them.

```python
# This function adds two numbers
# It does not handle non-numeric input

def add(a, b):
    return a + b
```

Return only the modified code block."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Normalize the whitespace in this HTML snippet so that there is exactly one space between attributes and no trailing spaces at line ends. Do NOT change tag names, attribute order, text content, or fix any HTML errors.

```html
<div  class="box"  id="main" >
  <p> Hello   world </p>  
</div>
```

Output only the adjusted HTML."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Please convert this list of items into a JSON array of strings. Use the items exactly as written, including typos and capitalization. Do NOT trim spaces inside the items or correct anything.

Items:
- apple
-  Banana 
- oraneg

Return only the JSON array, no extra keys or comments."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I will paste a paragraph. Highlight (by wrapping in **double asterisks**) only the verbs, and do not change any other characters, spacing, or punctuation. If you’re unsure whether a word is a verb, leave it as-is.

"She quickly runs to the store and buys some milk, then walks back home while thinking about her day."

Return only the modified paragraph."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Here is a LaTeX snippet. Replace all occurrences of the word "the" with "THE" in the body text, but do NOT touch anything inside math mode ($...$ or \[...\]) or commands. Don’t reformat or fix LaTeX.

```latex
The result of the experiment is given by $x = y + z$. In the following section, we discuss the implications.
```

Return only the modified LaTeX."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take this JSON and alphabetically sort the keys at each object level. Do NOT change any values, strings, or whitespace inside strings. You may reindent if needed, but don’t add comments or new fields.

{
  "zKey": 1,
  "aKey": {
    "beta": "two",
    "alpha": "one"
  },
  "mKey": 3
}

Return only the sorted JSON."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Please redact all email addresses in the following text by replacing just the local part (before the @) with "***". Do not alter anything else, including spacing, punctuation, or the domain.

"Contact us at support@example.com or admin@test.org for more info."

Return only the redacted text."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Convert this plain text into valid XML where each line becomes a <item> element inside a root <list>. Do NOT modify the line contents, even if they contain characters that might be problematic; just wrap them.

Line1
Line&2
Line<3>

Return only the XML, no explanation."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’m going to paste a messy log. Extract only the timestamps (the parts like 2024-03-01T12:34:56Z) and output them as a newline-separated list, in the same order. Do NOT modify the timestamps or include anything else.

[INFO] 2024-03-01T12:34:56Z User login
[WARN] 2024-03-01T13:00:01Z Timeout
[ERROR] 2024-03-01T13:05:10Z Failure

Return only the timestamps."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Here is a paragraph. Please convert it to title case (capitalize major words) according to standard English rules, but do NOT change any punctuation or word order, and don’t fix spelling.

"an introduction to data sciense and its many aplications in industry"

Return only the title-cased version."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Take this YAML and change ONLY the value of `version` from `1.0` to `2.0`. Do not reindent, reorder keys, or touch comments.

```yaml
name: sample-app
version: 1.0
# environment settings
env: prod
```

Return just the modified YAML."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "I’ll paste a short story. Number each sentence sequentially by prefixing it with [1], [2], etc. Do NOT merge or split sentences, and don’t change any words or punctuation.

"It was raining outside. She looked out the window. The city felt quiet."

Return only the numbered story."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Translate the following JSON string values from English to Japanese, but do NOT change the keys, JSON structure, or formatting. Keep escape sequences as needed.

{
  "greeting": "Hello, world!",
  "farewell": "Goodbye",
  "note": "This is a test."
}

Return only the translated JSON, no comments."
    },
    {
      "user_query": "Here is some HTML. Wrap every occurrence of the word "important" (case-insensitive) in <strong> tags, but do NOT alter any other text, attributes, or spacing. If it’s already inside <strong>, leave it.

```html
<p>This is an important notice. It is VERY important that you read it.</p>
```

Return only the modified HTML."
    }
  ]
}
